orl_sentence: Years ago while lying in my hammock and drinking JB from the bottle , I [MASK] my dog dragging something under the fence .
[MASK] looking at it carefully , to my disappointment , I realized it was the next-door neighbor's 10-year-old daughter's rabbit .

I know today [MASK] be no different .

Within the hour the neighbor's car pulled in as usual and out came the little girl , [MASK] as usual she headed straight for the cage .
Only this time did she stop about six feet away and [MASK] D-A-D-D-Y- !
! Her father , [MASK] , stood looking at the cage .

Being the good neighbor , I rushed to the fence and asked if there was anything I could do . Her father less than calmly shouted , What kind of [MASK] person would dig up a little girl's dead rabbit and put it back in its cage ?
On the moving day to our new house , my mom hoped she would look good for the new neighbors . So she went to the [MASK] centre to get her brown hair straightened .
On the moving day to our new house , my mom hoped she would look good for the new neighbors . So she went to the beauty centre to get her brown hair [MASK] .
The hairdresser was not [MASK] and made my mom's hair curly .
My mom [MASK] the whole way to our house , My hair , my hair--don't look !
When she got home , she put a(n) [MASK] and magical potato pot on her head .
This magical potato pot came from the kitchen [MASK] .
It looked like a(n) [MASK] pot , but it was really magical .
Next , my mom [MASK] to go shopping to buy things for our new house , so she went to a supermarket .
Next , my mom needed to go shopping to buy things for our new house , [MASK] she went to a supermarket .
The people there looked at her [MASK] as if she had come from the outer space .
Then she went to the post office to [MASK] a letter to my grandparents .
The people there thought she was [MASK] .
They looked at her just the same as the people at the supermarket did . She went and [MASK] many more hairdressers to help her with her crazy curly hair !
None of them could fix her hair . She [MASK] to all the hairdressers , You call yourselves hairdressers---you're just not seeing my crazy hair !
None of them could fix her hair . She complained to all the hairdressers , You [MASK] yourselves hairdressers---you're just not seeing my crazy hair !
Then she rushed home . When she got home , my mom screamed to the [MASK] , You magical potato pot !

You just can't do anything ! Then , my mom went to the bathroom , and she took down the pot . WOW ! My mom screamed , MY HAIR IS ALL STRAIGHT ! She made a(n) [MASK] to the pot and said , You are really magical .
I am sorry it is my [MASK] .
The pot said , You mean you have done something [MASK] to me ?
